1) Installation
---------------

Unpack to some directory ($BEAR in following)

Required perl modules:

	* DBI
	* DBD::SQLite
	* FreezeThaw
	* XML::Simple
	* IPC::ShareLite


2) Running
----------

2a) Meta-Data daemon

	bash$ cd $BEAR
	bash$ mdata/mdata.pl 


